&lt;h1 id="why-startups-condense-in-america"&gt;Why Startups Condense in America&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;May 2006&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;(This essay is derived from a keynote at Xtech.)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Startups happen in clusters. There are a lot of them in Silicon Valley and Boston, and few in Chicago or Miami. A country that wants startups will probably also have to reproduce whatever makes these clusters form.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>